283
00:16:29,288 --> 00:16:31,690
<i>When he said,</i>
<i>"That red won't come out very well,"</i>

284
00:16:31,757 --> 00:16:34,526
<i>I was like, "That's such</i>
<i>a professional thing to say."</i>

285
00:16:35,094 --> 00:16:38,664
If there's a date event,
I'd have to write down Taeheon's name.

286
00:16:38,731 --> 00:16:41,266
Mmm. I wouldn't hesitate to choose him.

287
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:44,470
I'd love to see some art
or architecture with Taeheon.

288
00:16:46,772 --> 00:16:48,807
- His tone is so funny.
- So funny.

289
00:16:48,874 --> 00:16:50,809
- He's nonchalant.
- That's Hiroya's style.

290
00:16:50,876 --> 00:16:51,777
BOWLING TOURNAMENT!

291
00:16:51,844 --> 00:16:54,546
- I'm so excited!
- Bowling! Bowling!

292
00:16:54,613 --> 00:16:56,815
- Hey! Bowling…
- <i>Ah, in a Sazae-san style.</i>

293
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:59,151
PALACE BOWL

