296
00:17:04,356 --> 00:17:05,824
- Sounds good!
- I won't be able to go.

297
00:17:05,891 --> 00:17:08,727
- Why not? You never know.
- You never know! Anything could happen.

298
00:17:10,462 --> 00:17:11,797
There it goes!

299
00:17:11,864 --> 00:17:13,766
- Oh, that's super good!
- Looking good!

300
00:17:17,236 --> 00:17:19,571
<i>Hey! I'm done caring 'bout…</i>

301
00:17:19,638 --> 00:17:21,874
- Oh, nice.
- Beautiful.

302
00:17:22,508 --> 00:17:24,843
There you are!

303
00:17:27,212 --> 00:17:29,181
I know, right?
He's way ahead so far, but…

304
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:33,786
- Hey! Wow!
- Wow.

305
00:17:33,852 --> 00:17:35,954
Huwei's really good at it too.

306
00:17:38,991 --> 00:17:41,460
I'm so bad. Maybe I should go home.

307
00:17:42,995 --> 00:17:44,863
- You were so hyped.
- I'm going.

308
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:47,900
<i>Oh, boy, I'll take</i>
<i>Everything on the menu…</i>

309
00:17:47,966 --> 00:17:49,768
Nice! Very good, very good!

310
00:17:50,502 --> 00:17:52,237
- Whoa!
- Wow, amazing.

311
00:17:52,738 --> 00:17:54,473
- I think I can hit 140.
- For sure.

312
00:17:57,476 --> 00:17:59,378
- Yay!
- Nice.

