00:18:05,150 --> 00:18:07,286
Those went down in such a crazy way!

314
00:18:07,352 --> 00:18:09,188
How do you even knock them down?

315
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:11,490
<i>I don't care about what others say</i>

316
00:18:11,557 --> 00:18:13,826
<i>Hey! Don't worry…</i>

317
00:18:13,892 --> 00:18:16,962
- Aah! Finally got a strike.
- Wow! Amazing.

318
00:18:17,029 --> 00:18:18,597
- That was amazing.
- Good job.

319
00:18:18,664 --> 00:18:20,699
Kazuyuki's really good.

320
00:18:21,366 --> 00:18:23,735
- All right!
- It's over for me.

321
00:18:23,802 --> 00:18:25,637
- Did you hit 170?
- I hit 170.

322
00:18:25,704 --> 00:18:27,406
- That's high!
- Go home!

