00:18:28,474 --> 00:18:30,075
- You're too good at this.
- Go home!

324
00:18:30,142 --> 00:18:32,077
Go home?

325
00:18:32,144 --> 00:18:34,480
No words. I am completely defeated.

326
00:18:34,546 --> 00:18:36,582
- Congratulations!
- Thanks!

327
00:18:36,648 --> 00:18:38,550
<i>Kazuyuki has a hidden talent.</i>

328
00:18:38,617 --> 00:18:40,052
- You're too good.
- Yeah.

329
