469
00:26:54,446 --> 00:26:56,348
I'll give my spot to Hiroya
who came in second.

470
00:26:57,048 --> 00:26:59,618
Thanks. Yeah. Thanks.

471
00:26:59,684 --> 00:27:02,854
But I'm glad you came
to that conclusion in the end.

472
00:27:03,488 --> 00:27:05,957
- It's a huge decision, after all.
