00:42:26,677 --> 00:42:28,045
Coming out…

807
00:42:29,413 --> 00:42:31,248
isn't just about me

808
00:42:32,283 --> 00:42:34,385
being attracted to men,

809
00:42:34,451 --> 00:42:37,488
it's more about the fact that I won't,

810
00:42:38,322 --> 00:42:41,025
um, be able to give him grandkids.

811
00:42:41,692 --> 00:42:43,060
Yeah, so…

812
00:42:45,963 --> 00:42:47,765
Mmm.

813
00:42:47,831 --> 00:42:49,767
<i>He's really struggling with it.</i>

814
00:42:50,267 --> 00:42:52,403
<i>They're all in the same boat.</i>

815
00:42:53,203 --> 00:42:55,406
I think my dad

816
00:42:56,073 --> 00:42:57,641
would be really sad

817
00:42:58,342 --> 00:43:00,377
about not being able to see my kids.

818
00:43:01,245 --> 00:43:03,080
I think he'd be disappointed.

819
00:43:08,185 --> 00:43:09,386
I can't tell him.

820
00:43:11,255 --> 00:43:15,292
It's not like I think anyone is to blame.

821
00:43:15,359 --> 00:43:18,395
I don't think there's anything
wrong with me either.

822
00:43:18,462 --> 00:43:21,265
But when I think about coming out,

823
00:43:21,332 --> 00:43:25,035
I think about what my parents
had done for me.

824
00:43:25,102 --> 00:43:27,938
When I was little,
I'd get sick and had a high fever,

825
00:43:28,005 --> 00:43:29,940
and my parents would try
to stay up all night,

826
00:43:30,007 --> 00:43:32,209
holding my hand until I fell asleep.

827
00:43:32,943 --> 00:43:37,014
And when I accomplished something,
even something small,

828
00:43:37,081 --> 00:43:40,317
