I just feel so guilty.

830
00:43:46,090 --> 00:43:48,025
It's not that anyone's to blame.

831
00:43:48,859 --> 00:43:53,464
I'm open about it now.
I learned how to be open about it, so…

832
00:43:53,530 --> 00:43:57,401
I don't want you to feel like you have
to live up to someone's expectations.

833
00:43:59,136 --> 00:44:03,307
You might feel guilty,
but that's because of who you are.

834
00:44:03,374 --> 00:44:05,175
You're a kind person.

835
00:44:05,242 --> 00:44:08,979
I mean, just because
you were born from them,

836
00:44:09,046 --> 00:44:12,850
